<section class="intro">
  <h1>Matt Riel <span class="job-title">Front-End Designer</span></h1>
  <p>Hello. I'm Matt, a Front End Designer. I love to design and create products with simple, long lasting designs
    that are accessible for everyone. </p>
  <p>I have previously worked for both non-profit institutions and start ups, providing expertise in design,
    usability, accessibility, and technology. </p>
  <p>My belief is that having a clear message to drive straightforward transparent content leads to a simple
    timeless design where the product shines. </p>
</section>
<section class="exp section-spacing">
  {%- for exp in collections.exp | reverse -%}
